SumFunction - 程序包 SumFunction
This package was created using MATLAB Compiler SDK.
SumFunction(List, List) - 类 中的方法SumFunction.Class1
Provides the interface for calling the SumFunction MATLAB function where the first argument, an instance of List, receives the output of the MATLAB function and the second argument, also an instance of List, provides the input to the MATLAB function.
SumFunction(Object[], Object[]) - 类 中的方法SumFunction.Class1
Provides the interface for calling the SumFunction MATLAB function where the first argument, an Object array, receives the output of the MATLAB function and the second argument, also an Object array, provides the input to the MATLAB function.
SumFunction(int, Object...) - 类 中的方法SumFunction.Class1
Provides the standard interface for calling the SumFunction MATLAB function with 2 comma-separated input arguments.
SumFunction(int, Object...) - 接口 中的方法SumFunction.Class1Remote
Provides the standard interface for calling the SumFunction MATLAB function with 2 input arguments.
